1 AN ACT
2 MAKING APPROPRIATIONS FROM THE PUBLIC PROJECT REVOLVING FUND
3 TO THE DRINKING WATER STATE REVOLVING LOAN FUND, LOCAL
4 GOVERNMENT PLANNING FUND AND CULTURAL AFFAIRS FACILITIES
5 INFRASTRUCTURE FUND.
6
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF NEW MEXICO:
8 SECTION 1. APPROPRIATIONS.--
9 A. The following amounts are appropriated from the
10 public project revolving fund to the following funds:
11 (1) six million two hundred fifty thousand
12 dollars ($6,250,000) to the drinking water state revolving
13 loan fund for expenditure in fiscal year 2027 and subsequent
14 fiscal years to provide state matching funds for federal Safe
15 Drinking Water Act of 1974 projects and to carry out the
16 purposes of the Drinking Water State Revolving Loan Fund Act;
17 (2) two million dollars ($2,000,000) to the
18 local government planning fund for expenditure in fiscal year
19 2027 and subsequent fiscal years to carry out the purposes of
the fund; and
20
